  completed prospective, adaptively randomized study in heavily pretreated
  NSCLC patients that mandated tumor profiling with "real-time" biopsies,
  taking a substantial step toward realizing personalized lung cancer therapy
  by integrating real-time molecular laboratory findings in delineating
  specific patient populations for individualized treatment.%
