    \field{abstract}{%
    BACKGROUND We assessed the efficacy and safety of programmed cell death 1
  (PD-1) inhibition with pembrolizumab in patients with advanced non-small-cell
  lung cancer enrolled in a phase 1 study. We also sought to define and
  validate an expression level of the PD-1 ligand 1 (PD-L1) that is associated
